list.name: Default
list.comment:
Added SensorHelper to detect azimuth/pitch/roll, LocationProvider to save GPS coordinates to image, menus to gallery & slideshow, and changed some icons. Can now select options (info, delete, rotate, etc.) for an image if image is pressed for a second. Rotations are not updated in the gallery yet for some reason.
Added some sample images that could be useful for the gallery's toolbar (like pencil/edit and trash/delete icons).

task.summary: Added more features, including adjustments to permissions, hiding UI, and using SparseArray for loading color filters.
Made significant improvements overall in gallery design, including a fullscreen preview of images and being able to rotate the screen in the gallery. Fixed some minor permission loopholes.
Fixed leaked views with permissions and added handling for "Don't ask again" option when requesting permission.

MESSAGE.value: Added more features, including adjustments to permissions and hiding UI.
Added more features, including adjustments to permissions, hiding UI, and using SparseArray for loading color filters.
Made significant improvements overall in gallery design, including a fullscreen preview of images and being able to rotate the screen in the gallery. Fixed some minor permission loopholes.
Fixed leaked views with permissions and added handling for "Don't ask again" option when requesting permission.
